search: rest hooks vs websockets


http://iot-datamodels.blogspot.ca/2013/05/event-models-for-restful-apis.html

http://www.slideshare.net/rossmason/realtime-apis
    push vs streaming: 
        push: subscription and filter, asynchronous, drawback reliability complicated
        streaming: keep the connection open, request-response, 
                                      drawback harder to implement durable connection 
    realtime techs: transport: comet, websocket
                    protocol with formal pub/sub semantics: XMPP, Bayeux, STOMP
                    protocol adhoc: JSON
                    push: PubSubhubbub, Web Hooks
    real use:    salesforce    comet
                 facebook      pubsubhubbub
                 instagram     ad hoc (webhooks/pubsubhubbub)
                 twitter       ad hoc (comet)
                 pubnub        ad hoc
                 superfeedr    XMPP
                 pusher        ad hoc (websockets)
    rossmason mulesoft mule-streaming-api-demo



